  {
    "function_v0": {
      "doc": "Get all position values for an account from a real Blend pool.\\n\\nCalled by PositionRegistry as:\\n`adapter.get_all_pos(account, oracle_registry, accounting_token)`\\n\\nSteps:\\n1. Call `pool.get_reserve_list()` \\xe2\\x86\\x92 Vec<Address> (index \\xe2\\x86\\x92 asset)\\n2. Call `pool.get_positions(account)` \\xe2\\x86\\x92 Positions { collateral, supply, liabilities }\\n3. For each (index, b_tokens) in supply + collateral:\\na. Get asset = reserve_list[index]\\nb. Call `pool.get_reserve(asset)` \\xe2\\x86\\x92 b_rate, decimals\\nc. Convert: underlying = b_tokens * b_rate / RATE_SCALAR\\nd. Price via oracle_registry.get_price_pair(asset, accounting_token)\\n4. For each (index, d_tokens) in liabilities: same with d_rate, is_debt=true\\n5. Returns Vec<PositionValue>",
      "name": "get_all_pos",
      "inputs": [
        {
          "doc": "",
          "name": "account",
          "type_": "address"
        },
        {
          "doc": "",
          "name": "oracle_registry",
          "type_": "address"
        },
        {
          "doc": "",
          "name": "accounting_token",
          "type_": "address"
        }
      ],
      "outputs": [
        {
          "vec": {
            "element_type": {
              "udt": {
                "name": "PositionValue"
              }
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  },
